section.def:
decree
                (判令) means a decree nisi of divorce, and a decree
            of nullity or judicial separation;

election
                (選擇) means an election under rule 3 to
            take fixed costs in accordance with these rules;

Form
                (表格) means a form specified in the Second
                Schedule;

subsection.def:
*commencement
                    date (實施日期) means the date on which
                the Amendment Rules come into operation;

section.def:
Ordinance
                    (條例) means the Matrimonial Causes Ordinance
                    (Cap. 179);
